N. Lafourche Cons., Levee & Drain. Dist. -- 6 Mills Renewal - BOC - 30 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
North Lafourche Conservation, Levee and Drainage District Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall North Lafourche Conservation, Levee and Drainage District (the "District") be authorized to levy a special tax of six (6) mills on all the property subject to taxation in said District for a period of thirty (30) years, beginning with the year 2019 and ending with the year 2048 (an estimated $2,100,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for the purpose of constructing and maintaining necessary levees, levee drainage, flood protection, hurricane flood protection and for all other purposes incidental thereto?
